_sText:
My first Bomb/Defuse map.
It's medium size and for 20 players.
It has dev textures as you can see and many people like them.
It's balanced, at least I hope so because I didn't play with anyone but I played it myself and I think it should be balacned. Bomb spots are close for both teams and I made few meet-spots where teams can meet and wipe out.
Can't tell much, download it and try it.
Thanks and enjoy,
Rapt.
